data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Locust Grove, just minutes away from local restaurants and shopping including Tanger Outlets. It also comes with several upgrades including a new water heater (2022), brand new carpet (2024), updated kitchen (2019) and flooring (2020), new paint (2024) and updated fireplace and stairs. This stunning 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom brick-front residence offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and functionality. Upon entering, you are greeted by a spacious main level featuring a living room, family room, formal dining room, kitchen, and a convenient half bath. The kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, a breakfast area, and a pantry. The upper level contains all four bedrooms and two full bathrooms, providing privacy away from the main living spaces. The primary suite has a generous layout with an en suite bathroom including a luxurious soaking tub, a separate shower, and a huge walk-in closet. Additionally, there is a full laundry room on the upper level which provides an extra level of convenience. Outside, the home showcases a two-car attached garage and a charming back patio, perfect for entertaining guests or simply enjoying the beautiful outdoors. With its desirable location, spacious layout, and luxurious amenities, this property offers a lifestyle of comfort and convenience that is second to none. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exquisite residence your new home sweet home.
